body:
I find the bugs come from the vs2015. When I update the vs2015 to vs2015update3 version , It compiles OK.
I suggest that the instructions ( (https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/tree/master/tensorflow/contrib/cmake )  need to emphasize the use of **vs2015 update3**
